  <description>
    Generic hexacopter (6-rotor) model with full sensor suite.
    Higher payload capacity and redundancy compared to the quadcopter.
    Sensors: IMU, GPS, barometer, magnetometer, camera, depth camera, LiDAR.
  </description>
</model>
